{"tid":1651611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[危機意識post] 聽晚要小心","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T13:08:45.000Z","uid":53673,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43ad8c9f0ccb100011928ded95dfad3f8f4ed645","tid":1651611,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"聽晚可能發生既事：<br />\n<br />\n集會前：<br />\n- 港鐵關站<br />\n- 巴士改道<br />\n- 瘋狂搜身，搜到gear即拉<br />\n- 水炮車、裝甲車，狗車到場<br />\n<br />\n集會途中：<br />\n- 黑警突然要求主辦者提早結束集會<br />\n- 黑警突然舉黃旗<br />\n- 黑警拋密線射催淚彈/藍威寶入集會場地內<br />\n- 直升機於上空監察或灑螢光粉<br />\n- 黑警突然乘民用車輛衝入集會場地內根據《禁止蒙面規例》拘捕蒙面/戴口罩人士<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">於集會內既黑警臥底突然行動，根據《禁止蒙面規例》拘捕蒙面/戴口罩人士，集會人士走都走唔到</span><br />\n- 拘捕遊行舉辦者及糾察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集會後：<br />\n- 搜查巴士、黨鐵、電車、小巴、渡輪，其中可能集中搜查<span style=\"color: red;\">走佬快線</span>（例如104線）<br />\n- 於鷹君中心、紅隧口、東隧口、西隧口、大欖隧道口設路障<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">進入商場（例如ifc）或私人地方</span>濫捕<br />\n- 黑警利用民用車輛巡邏或跟蹤接放學車，一見黑衫即落車拉<br />\n- 拘捕遊行舉辦者及糾察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手brainstorming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：淆底和理非"},{"pid":"8e0fb996995f4e81ddcd5f6622296466c5e354ab","tid":1651611,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"【18禁】班狗平時係威係勢 原來不過係賤犬一條<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651603</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd915d08e78cfe0017f2c6198225df34f83f9b96","tid":1651611,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f6cafd7f29539c110ba4808900c0ad2e593875","tid":1651611,"